=== 聯合王國 ===
2011年2月，琼斯应邀参加[[英国国防联盟|英国国防联盟]]在[[卢顿|卢顿]]举行的集会，在這次集會上他表达了對伊斯兰极端主义的看法。英国[[反法西斯主義|反法西斯主義]]同盟对此表示抗议并举行反对琼斯的示威；另更有反[[极端主义|极端主义]]组织“希望不恨”向時任[[內政大臣_(英國)|英國内政大臣]]请愿，要求英国禁止琼斯入境。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Koran-protest pastor Terry Jones invited to UK rally|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-11977945|newspaper=BBC News|date=2010-12-12|accessdate=2021-04-07|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101105431/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-11977945|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=US pastor Terry Jones banned from entering UK|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-12231832|newspaper=BBC News|date=2011-01-20|accessdate=2021-04-07|language=en-GB|archive-date=2018-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181013173707/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-12231832|dead-url=no}}</ref>

